---
title: Mandarin Orange Trout with Asparagus plus Golden Rice, Dill Crème Fraîche & Lemon
description: Let your oven do the heavy lifting in this 30-minute baking sheet meal! You’ll roast buttery dill-seasoned trout alongside asparagus, shingling the fish with lemon and mandarin orange slices for a sunny presentation. Serve atop bowls of garlicky, turmeric-tinged rice and drizzle with lemony dill crème fraîche for a delicious, citrus-forward supper.
